## Decisions Summary (Locked ✅)

| Decision | Choice |
|---|---|
| **Frontend** | Next.js (App Router) — CSR where it makes sense (e.g., embedding), SSR optional |
| **Backend** | Express — **separate microservice** for heavy audio processing |
| **Dev Environment** | **Docker Compose** — both services containerized |
| **AI SDK** | Vercel AI SDK (`ai` + `@ai-sdk/google`) |
| **Phase 1 Models** | Gemini 2.5 Flash + `text-multilingual-embedding-002` |
| **Future Models** | Qwen2-Audio 7B (HuggingFace Endpoints or GCP Cloud Run free credits) |
| **Vector DB** | Pinecone (metadata includes `tags`) |
| **Audio Storage** | PWA + File System Access API |
| **Client Encoding** | `lamejs` for MP3 encoding |
| **Recording Limit** | 45 minutes (warning at 40 min) |
| **Recording Controls** | Pause / Resume / Stop |
| **Audio Formats** | WAV, MP3, M4A, Apple MPEG-4 Audio, MP4, WebM |
| **Architecture** | Split: Next.js (frontend + light API) ↔ Express (audio processing) |

