| Feature | Implementation |
|---|---|
| **Pause** | `mediaRecorder.pause()` → freeze timer, freeze waveform, blink timestamp |
| **Resume** | `mediaRecorder.resume()` → restart timer, reactivate waveform |
| **Stop** | `mediaRecorder.stop()` → trigger DSP pipeline |
| **Timer** | Shows `elapsed / 45:00` format with progress bar |
| **40-min warning** | Progress bar turns orange, "5 minutes remaining" badge pulses |
| **45-min auto-stop** | `setTimeout` at 45 min → auto-triggers stop + toast notification |

