### v2: RAG Chat + Smart Gallery

> Goal: Query your recordings with natural language + beautiful gallery

| Task | Detail |
|---|---|
| RAG Chat page (`/chat`) | Streaming responses via Vercel AI SDK `useChat()` hook |
| Gallery page (`/`) | InsightCard grid with mood-based gradients |
| Detail page (`/insight/[id]`) | Full transcript, summary, Gold Nuggets, snippet playback |
| Search | Client-side filter on title, transcript, tags |
| Mood theming | Dynamic background gradient per insight mood |

RAG endpoint uses `streamText()` for real-time answer streaming:

```typescript
// web/src/app/api/query/route.ts
import { streamText, embed } from "ai";
import { google } from "@ai-sdk/google";

export async function POST(req: Request) {
  const { query } = await req.json();
  
  const { embedding } = await embed({
    model: google.textEmbeddingModel("text-multilingual-embedding-002"),
    value: query,
  });

  const matches = await pineconeIndex.query({
    vector: embedding, topK: 5, includeMetadata: true,
  });

  const context = matches.matches?.map(m => 
    `Title: ${m.metadata?.title}\nTags: ${m.metadata?.tags}\nTranscript: ${m.metadata?.transcript}`
  ).join("\n---\n");

  const result = streamText({
    model: google("gemini-2.5-flash"),
    prompt: `Answer based ONLY on context:\n${context}\n\nQuestion: ${query}`,
  });

  return result.toDataStreamResponse();
}
```

